[
  {
    "startTime": 5.538,
    "endTime": 7.006,
    "text": "- Helena.    - Cornelia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.139,
    "endTime": 7.74,
    "text": "It is good to see you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.073,
    "endTime": 11.108,
    "text": "It has been far too long since we have gathered our banners together in war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.177,
    "endTime": 11.878,
    "text": "Hear, hear!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.112,
    "endTime": 14.08,
    "text": "I'd like to call this council of motherhood to order."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.113,
    "endTime": 16.349,
    "text": "We must band together to vanquish our foe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.382,
    "endTime": 18.184,
    "text": "Like the great battle of potty training."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.317,
    "endTime": 21.419,
    "text": "I could not have conquered the porcelain throne without your Elmo sticker chart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.42,
    "endTime": 23.623,
    "text": "But now far greater evil has come upon us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.956,
    "endTime": 25.191,
    "text": "Is it summiting Mount Laundry?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.224,
    "endTime": 25.725,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.759,
    "endTime": 27.26,
    "text": "Is it toddler sleep negotiations?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.693,
    "endTime": 29.628,
    "text": "No. These evils will always exist in our world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.395,
    "endTime": 31.431,
    "text": "Well then, what is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.564,
    "endTime": 32.332,
    "text": "Surely together..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.365,
    "endTime": 34.133,
    "text": "The grocery trip with small children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.166,
    "endTime": 36.235,
    "text": "Devil incarnate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.268,
    "endTime": 37.203,
    "text": "It is right that you called us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.236,
    "endTime": 39.172,
    "text": "An attack falls upon me weekly, Your Grace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.205,
    "endTime": 41.107,
    "text": "But this is different."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.44,
    "endTime": 43.675999999999995,
    "text": "This the semi-annual Costco stock up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.445,
    "endTime": 49.115,
    "text": "This is my first battle going to Costco with three children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.248,
    "endTime": 51.583999999999996,
    "text": "Oh, two children is a battle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.617,
    "endTime": 54.253,
    "text": "Three children is war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.286,
    "endTime": 55.154,
    "text": "What can be done?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.187,
    "endTime": 59.492,
    "text": "Your defeat is inevitable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.525,
    "endTime": 62.428,
    "text": "My scouts tell me this is the current layout of Costco."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.461,
    "endTime": 64.464,
    "text": "And be wary, I will need two carts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.497,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "One cart is a battle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.133,
    "endTime": 68.134,
    "text": "Two carts is war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.167,
    "endTime": 70.036,
    "text": "Okay,  Helena, we get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.069,
    "endTime": 70.436,
    "text": "Do you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.469,
    "endTime": 71.00399999999999,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.237,
    "endTime": 73.472,
    "text": "Why not just send your husband to the front lines?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.406,
    "endTime": 75.37400000000001,
    "text": "You coward!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.407,
    "endTime": 78.475,
    "text": "He always falls prey to the sweet sounds of the Vitamix demonstration."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.444,
    "endTime": 79.679,
    "text": "Perhaps if..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.712,
    "endTime": 82.215,
    "text": "I ask for diapers, he comes back with four dozen muffins!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.248,
    "endTime": 83.049,
    "text": "You have your list?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.082,
    "endTime": 87.22,
    "text": "Obviously."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.153,
    "endTime": 93.45700000000001,
    "text": "Your best chance is to take it one section at a time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.425,
    "endTime": 94.25999999999999,
    "text": "Produce first..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.393,
    "endTime": 95.328,
    "text": "Are you mad?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.361,
    "endTime": 98.562,
    "text": "With children in the cart, the bananas will be carnage by the end!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.064,
    "endTime": 100.93199999999999,
    "text": "True. Produce is a vulnerable area."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.1,
    "endTime": 102.235,
    "text": "What weapons do you have?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.268,
    "endTime": 103.636,
    "text": "Fruit snacks and Goldfish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.669,
    "endTime": 106.572,
    "text": "But for this conflict, I shall wield the holy grail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.64,
    "endTime": 109.375,
    "text": "The iPad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.408,
    "endTime": 110.209,
    "text": "And risk a crack?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.242,
    "endTime": 112.245,
    "text": "That's a risk I'm willing to take."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.278,
    "endTime": 114.57900000000001,
    "text": "I mean, if you feel comfortable with that amount of screen time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.58,
    "endTime": 117.416,
    "text": "Save the mom guilt for the battlefield, Cornelia!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.449,
    "endTime": 118.551,
    "text": "This is foolish!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.584,
    "endTime": 123.286,
    "text": "Three children sharing one iPad, you'll be on borders of meltdown territory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.489,
    "endTime": 126.991,
    "text": "Well, then retreat back to food court fortress! They will obey for a churro!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.059,
    "endTime": 129.095,
    "text": "Sugar and screens cannot be the way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.128,
    "endTime": 129.595,
    "text": "What other..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.829,
    "endTime": 131.13,
    "text": "Enough arguing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.163,
    "endTime": 134.604,
    "text": "If we cannot agree, we must call on ancient wisdom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.837,
    "endTime": 140.13899999999998,
    "text": "Hello, mighty grandmother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.172,
    "endTime": 141.14,
    "text": "How many children?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.173,
    "endTime": 141.941,
    "text": "Three, m'lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.608,
    "endTime": 144.377,
    "text": "In my day, I had eight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.41,
    "endTime": 145.71099999999998,
    "text": "You left them in the car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.044,
    "endTime": 148.44500000000002,
    "text": "I cracked a window. Nobody cared back then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.514,
    "endTime": 151.15,
    "text": "- But what should I do now, oh wise one? - Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.383,
    "endTime": 154.82000000000002,
    "text": "Consider the belt buckle, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.853,
    "endTime": 156.622,
    "text": "You only have to use it once..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.955,
    "endTime": 157.59,
    "text": "Okay, I think we're good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.623,
    "endTime": 159.559,
    "text": "You won't hear my words of wisdoms?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.659,
    "endTime": 161.827,
    "text": "If you would only..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.86,
    "endTime": 164.29700000000003,
    "text": "Know that the water is giving the children chicken pox."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.33,
    "endTime": 167.26600000000002,
    "text": "- Yeah.   - Oh, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.299,
    "endTime": 168.334,
    "text": "The time has come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.367,
    "endTime": 169.402,
    "text": "I must away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.435,
    "endTime": 171.604,
    "text": "Remember, stick to your list."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.637,
    "endTime": 173.138,
    "text": "Resist the impulse buy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.272,
    "endTime": 174.40699999999998,
    "text": "Even if it's dark chocolate covered almonds?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.84,
    "endTime": 176.80700000000002,
    "text": "- Ooh!   - Yes! Be strong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.875,
    "endTime": 180.077,
    "text": "Thank you, wise leaders. I feel ready."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.145,
    "endTime": 181.38000000000002,
    "text": "Go with speed, friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.313,
    "endTime": 185.117,
    "text": "May fortune smile upon you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.15,
    "endTime": 186.085,
    "text": "To battle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.118,
    "endTime": 189.555,
    "text": "Kids, get your shoes on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.588,
    "endTime": 192.191,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.224,
    "endTime": 197.16299999999998,
    "text": "I shall bring you the Costco receipt on a spike!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.196,
    "endTime": 201.197,
    "text": "Oh, I forgot! Costco lets you order online, and they'll just deliver it to your car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.2,
    "endTime": 205.20399999999998,
    "text": "Eh, next time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.237,
    "endTime": 207.406,
    "text": "Mothers, subscribe!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.439,
    "endTime": 209.075,
    "text": "Like this video!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.108,
    "endTime": 211.177,
    "text": "Share this video!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.21,
    "endTime": 213.512,
    "text": "Comment upon this video!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.545,
    "endTime": 214.713,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.746,
    "endTime": 217.383,
    "text": "When was a time that your mother left you in the car?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.416,
    "endTime": 219.48499999999999,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.518,
    "endTime": 221.12,
    "text": "Did your mom do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.153,
    "endTime": 221.554,
    "text": "She did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.587,
    "endTime": 222.587,
    "text": "13 times."
  }
]